
[1]correctly

   CORRECTLY, adv. In a correct manner; in conformity with truth, justice,
   rectitude, or propriety; according to a standard; agreeable to a copy
   or original; exactly; accurately; without fault, or error; as, to
   behave correctly; to write, speak or think correctly; to judge
   correctly.
